// Dragnet [Container]: dragnet-container-2026-1697 — Vulnerable Base Image Pull
// Status: deprecated | Level: critical | ID: 83c3aabe-449e-50a1-9a10-8e1809460bd2

#event_simpleName=*
| (ImageFileName = *amazonlinux:1* OR ImageFileName = *redhat/ubi9:*)
| table([timestamp, ComputerName])
| limit(1000)
